title: Past Players to Add to 2019 Rosters
itunes:title: Past Players to Add to 2019 Rosters
description:
Dave Dameshek is joined in Studio 66 by Cole Wright for a brand new DDFP! The guys start out joking about how their workouts have been lately (14:05) followed by some running back talk as Ezekiel Elliott and Melvin Gordon prepare to holdout from camp (18:50). Next, Shek, Cole and Spaghetti add a past player to each of NFC teams roster to help improve them (26:00). Lastly, the group looks back on the career of Mark Sanchez and how we'd view him differently if he brought one of those AFC championship Jets teams to the Super Bowl (1:13:47).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
